messages.messageBody:
You're alright and your message came through!
What it means (I think( is that someone on this list is using Microchip.com
as their internet provider and their ISP is objecting (for whatever reason)
to the Unschoolingdotcom emails.
Those emails have YOUR email address listed as the "From" source, so they
send you a note saying they don't like your email.
Fortunately, they have no influence over yahoogroups (I think, again.)
That's what I think's going on, anyway.
HeidiWD
